  <note reference-line="3" id="0">
    <original>sappurisūpassayo (sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet>, bhikkhave, cakkāni, yehi samannāgatānaṃ devamanussānaṃ catucakkaṃ vattati, yehi samannāgatā devamanussā nacirasseva mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇanti bhogesu. Katamāni cattāri? Patirūpadesavāso, sappurisāvassayo </snippet>
